On this site we start to share information about the ezx bootloader. Motorola eses a modified blob for the ezx phones. The modified source is available here: http://www.datenfreihafen.org/~stefan/EZX/a780-blob.tar.bz2

To enter the bootloader you need to press the camera and jogdial button and power on.

